name: Celestial Peaks of Ramelau
description: Towering mountains shrouded in mist, where the air is thin and the stars feel close enough to touch.

name: Enchanted Forests of Lautém
description: Ancient woodlands filled with bioluminescent plants and the whispers of unseen creatures.

name: Whispering Caves of Baucau
description: A network of caverns where echoes of the past reverberate through winding passages.

name: Shimmering Shores of Jaco Island
description: Pristine beaches with sand that glitters like stardust under the tropical sun.

name: Emerald Terraces of Bobonaro
description: Lush, stepped rice fields that cascade down hillsides in a mesmerizing display of green.

name: Ethereal Springs of Marobo
description: Steaming hot springs surrounded by mystical fog, said to have healing properties.

name: Misty Marshes of Covalima
description: Eerie wetlands where will-o'-wisps dance above the water and strange creatures lurk below.

name: Whispering Woodlands of Viqueque
description: A dense forest where the trees seem to murmur ancient secrets to those who listen closely.

name: Radiant Ruins of Maubisse
description: The remnants of an ancient civilization that glow with an otherworldly light at dusk.

name: Thundering Falls of Bandeira
description: A majestic waterfall whose roar can be heard for miles, creating rainbows in its mist.

name: Whispering Winds of Venilale
description: Rolling hills where the constant breeze carries whispers of forgotten tales.

name: Shimmering Sands of Com
description: A stretch of coastline where the sand sparkles with an unearthly glow under moonlight.

name: Misty Peaks of Matebian
description: Cloud-wreathed mountain summits where reality seems to blur at the edges.

name: Echoing Caverns of Lautém
description: A vast underground system where sounds reverberate in mysterious ways, sometimes answering back.

name: Enchanted Groves of Ermera
description: Secluded woodlands where the trees seem to shift positions when no one is looking.

name: Whispering Canyons of Manatuto
description: Deep ravines where the wind creates eerie melodies as it rushes through the rocks.

name: Radiant Pools of Liquiçá
description: A series of natural pools that glow with an inner light, especially under the full moon.

name: Whispering Willows of Ainaro
description: A grove of ancient willows whose leaves rustle with words from another time.

name: Shimmering Springs of Baucau
description: Crystal-clear water sources that seem to ripple with colors not found in nature.

name: Misty Moors of Manufahi
description: Expansive grasslands often covered in a thick, mysterious fog that never seems to lift.

name: Ethereal Falls of Ataúro
description: A cascading waterfall on a remote island that seems to defy gravity, flowing upwards at times.

name: Whispering Wetlands of Lospalos
description: Swampy areas where the reeds and grasses whisper warnings and guidance to travelers.

name: Radiant Reefs of Bikeli
description: Underwater coral formations that emit a soft, multicolored glow visible from the shore.

name: Misty Mangroves of Metinaro
description: A labyrinthine coastal forest perpetually shrouded in a ghostly mist.

name: Whispering Winds of Baguia
description: Windswept highlands where the constant breeze seems to carry messages from distant lands.
